rows.name:
Well, well, well! Have I got a beaut of
a drink for you! I worked in the service
of the high court, so I know my stuff!

rows.label: tlk43700142_01_msg0002
rows.name:
In fact, I'll give you a full refund if you
can keep a straight face! Gahaha!

rows.label: tlk43700142_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Good to see you, owner! As ever,
I provide only the most exquisite drinks,
based on my days at the high court!
